  pm3.2 $p |- ( ph -> ( ps -> ( ph /\ ps ) ) ) $=
    ( wa id ex ) ABABCZFDE $.

  ${
    sylib.1 $e |- ( ph -> ps ) $.
    sylib.2 $e |- ( ps <-> ch ) $.
    $( A mixed syllogism inference from an implication and a biconditional.
