    hbab1 $p |- ( y e. { x | ph } -> A. x y e. { x | ph } ) $=
      ( cv cab wcel wsb df-clab hbs1 hbxfrbi ) CDABEFABCGBACBHABCIJ $.

    $( Bound-variable hypothesis builder for a class abstraction.  (Contributed
