  ${
    $d x y $.
    $( Define the identity relation.  Definition 9.15 of [Quine] p. 64.  For
       example, 5 ` _I ` 5 and ` -. ` 4 ` _I ` 5.  (Contributed by NM,
       13-Aug-1995.) $)
