     (Read:  The restriction of ` A ` to ` B ` .) $)
  cres $a class ( A |` B ) $.

  $( Extend the definition of a class to include the image of a class.  (Read:
     The image of ` B ` under ` A ` .) $)
  cima $a class ( A " B ) $.

